


     FindFirst(31.0)	  ARP Programmers Manual       FindFirst(31.0)



     NAME
	  FindFirst - Search for multilevel pattern match

     SYNOPSIS
	  rc = FindFirst(pat, AnchorPath)
	   d0		   D0	 A0

     FUNCTION
	  This function	searchs	the filesystem for a first match to
	  pat.

     INPUTS
	  char *pat - pointer to an ascii string

	  struct AnchorPath *AnchorPath	- Point	to an initilized
		  AnchorPath structure.

     RESULT
	  rc - 0 if success, non-zero for any error.  the error
		  returns are in arpbase.[hi]

     BUGS
	  None known.

     SEE ALSO
	  FindNext(), FreeAnchorChain()

     AUTHOR
	  JAT


























